 Disney’s LBV has hosted the PGA Tour, the LPGA Tour and USGA events. Test your skills and fortitude at the demanding 7th hole with its challenging island green. Bundle with Disney’s Palm and Disney’s Magnolia (on site together less than 7 miles away by car) for three rounds of Disney magic and fun! Added Value Complimentary pre-round range balls included. They must be requested upon arrival at the pro shop. — Valid 1/1/2017 - 12/31/2026 Play any combination of 3 rounds of Disney Golf on 3 different days during the same trip and receive a $30 golf merchandise credit. The merchandise credit available only at pro-shop and cannot be exchanged for cash. The merchandise credit will be issued upon check-in on the 3rd day of golf at the pro-shop. — Valid 9/27/2024 - 9/25/2025 Play any combination of 3 rounds of Disney Golf on 3 different days during the same trip and receive a $30 golf merchandise credit. The merchandise credit available only at pro-shop and cannot be exchanged for cash. The merchandise credit will be issued upon check-in on the 3rd day of golf at the pro-shop. — Valid 9/26/2025 - 9/30/2026 Reviews Add a Comment {{starRating = review.Rating; ""}} Reviewed {{formatDate(review.Date)}} Reviewed {{formatDate(review.Date)}} {{formatDate(review.Date)}} {{review.Comment}} {{totalPages = findNumberOfPages(pager.totalItems/pager.selectedPageSize); ""}} « {{n}} » Disney's Lake Buena Vista Golf Course Restrictions & Fees Weather Policy: This golf course has a strict weather policy in place. Reservations are expected to be honored unless the course has been officially closed for the duration of the day due to inclement weather. No refunds will be given for weather that the customer deems too cold, too hot, or too windy. Anyone who begins play while it is raining will not be eligible for a refund. — 9/27/2021 - 12/31/2026 Frost Delays: In the event of a frost delay the golf course allows up to One hour of delay, in which no refunds will be given. Any delay that extends